dct_description_sm: Engraved & Printed ... by W. & A.K. Johnston Edinburgh.
Shows waterways, roads, railways, county boundaries, various place names (lakes, mountains, fjords).
Presence of Norway's Drammen railway line (1872) and absence of Røros and Østfold lines (1877-79) date this map between 1872 and 1877.
